UID:wDYfA1cZspyEOZGeQbKwc
SUMMARY:Open Mic Tuesdays at TIM's!
DTSTAMP:20260325T064626Z
DTSTART:20260408T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:Open Mic Night at Tim’s hosted by Levi said. Songs\, stand-up\,
	 stories\, puppets\, poetry\, first drafts\, last chances. All of it welco
	me. Signups start at 6:30 PM\, so get there early! The open mic slots kick
	 off at 7 PM \\(15 minutes each\\). Every Tuesday // no cover // food spec
	ials for performers.  Tuesday nights are our Rock-O-Taco Tuesdays\, which 
	means $2 off tacos and 1/2 off any tequila \\(shots or cocktails\, any teq
	uila brand\\) from open to close! Come even earlier to enjoy our stellar h
	appy hour from 4-6. See you at TIM's!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/even
	ts/#/details/open-mic-tuesdays-at-tim-s/18343114/2026-04-07T00\n\nFrom SEA
	today - Food & Drink
